'''湯瑪斯·史丹利·“湯姆”·霍蘭德'''（{{lang-en|Thomas Stanley "Tom" Holland}}，{{bd|1996年|6月1日}}<ref name=birth>''Births, Marriages & Deaths Index of England & Wales, 1916–2005'' at ancestry.com</ref> ）是一位英國男演員，憑藉於[[倫敦|倫敦]][[維多利亞皇宫劇院|維多利亞皇宫劇院]]的音樂劇《{{le|舞動人生音樂劇|Billy Elliot the Musical}}》中扮演主角比利·艾略特而成名。2012年出演描述[[南亞海嘯|南亞海嘯]]的電影《[[浩劫奇蹟|浩劫奇蹟]]》。2015年6月，霍蘭德獲選在[[漫威電影宇宙|漫威電影宇宙]]中飾演「[[蜘蛛人|蜘蛛人]]」彼得·帕克。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://marvel.com/news/movies/24758/sony_pictures_and_marvel_studios_find_their_spider-man_star_and_director|title=Sony Pictures and Marvel Studios Find Their 'Spider-Man' Star and Director|work=Marvel.com|date=2015-06-23|accessdate=2015-06-23|archive-date=2015-06-24|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ZWEoSWCY?url=http://marvel.com/news/movies/24758/sony_pictures_and_marvel_studios_find_their_spider-man_star_and_director|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Spiderman">{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/453025-tom-holland-is-the-new-spider-man-and-will-be-directed-by-jon-watts|title=Tom Holland is the New Spider-Man and Will be Directed by Jon Watts!|publisher=ComingSoon.net|last=Perry|first=Spencer|date=2015-06-23|access-date=2015-06-24|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108112412/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/453025-tom-holland-is-the-new-spider-man-and-will-be-directed-by-jon-watts|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==早期生活==
湯瑪斯·史丹利·霍蘭德<ref>{{cite web |title=Tom Holland: Who is the new Spider-Man? |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/newsbeat-33248311 |publisher=BBC News |access-date=2021-03-24 |date=2015-06-23}}</ref>1996年6月1日生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[泰晤士河畔金斯頓|泰晤士河畔金斯頓]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Famous birthdays for 1 June: Tom Holland, Heidi Klum|work=UPI|date=2018-06-01|access-date=2020-05-31|url=https://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/2018/06/01/Famous-birthdays-for-June-1-Tom-Holland-Heidi-Klum/5931527819297/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:QVH6-WKNM |title=Person Details for Thomas Stanley Holland, "England and Wales Birth Registration Index, 1837-2008" — FamilySearch.org |work=familysearch.org |access-date=2015-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614094150/https://familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:QVH6-WKNM |archive-date=2015-06-14 |url-status=live }}</ref>，攝影師妮可拉（{{lang|en|Nicola}}，娘家姓佛洛斯特）和喜劇演員兼作家{{le|多明尼克·霍蘭德|Dominic Holland}}之子<ref name="est">[https://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/london-life/meet-tom-holland-the-16yearold-star-of-the-impossible-8427023.html "Meet Tom Holland... the 16-year-old star of The Impossible"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701125828/http://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/london-life/meet-tom-holland-the-16yearold-star-of-the-impossible-8427023.html |date=2015-07-01 }}, standard.co.uk, 2012-12-20.</ref><ref name="sct">[http://www.scotsman.com/lifestyle/film/schoolboy-actor-tom-holland-finds-himself-in-oscar-contention-for-role-in-tsunami-drama-1-2702253 "Schoolboy actor Tom Holland finds himself in Oscar contention for role in tsunami drama"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130525223124/http://www.scotsman.com/lifestyle/film/schoolboy-actor-tom-holland-finds-himself-in-oscar-contention-for-role-in-tsunami-drama-1-2702253 |date=2013-05-25 }}, ''The Scotsman'', 2012-12-21</ref>。他有三個弟弟<ref name="est"/><ref name=bww>[http://westend.broadwayworld.com/article/Holland-and-Pflueger-Are-West-Ends-Two-New-Billy-Elliots-20080828 "Holland and Pflueger Are West End's Two New 'Billy Elliots'"], BroadwayWorld.com, 2008-08-28.</ref>。祖母來自愛爾蘭[[蒂珀雷里郡|蒂珀雷里郡]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.irishcentral.com/roots/genealogy/new-spiderman-tom-holland-says-ireland-is-absolutely-amazing |title=New Spiderman Tom Holland says Ireland is "absolutely amazing" |work=IrishCentral |date=2017-07-07 |access-date=2021-10-13 |url-status=live}}</ref>。

霍蘭德在倫敦西南部[[温布尔登_(伦敦)|温布尔登]]的{{le|唐黑德預備學校|Donhead Preparatory School}}接受教育<ref>[http://www.donhead.org.uk/assos_oldboysnews/Tom_Holland_to_play_Billy_Elliott.php "Tom Holland to play Billy Elliot"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100723065115/http://www.donhead.org.uk/assos_oldboysnews/Tom_Holland_to_play_Billy_Elliott.php |date=2010-07-23 }}, donhead.org.uk; accessed 2014-09-22</ref>。後就讀志願資助的耶穌會綜合學校{{le|溫布爾登學院|Wimbledon College}}，直到2012年12月<ref>{{cite web |url=http://people.com/movies/spider-man-homecoming-tom-holland-talks-being-bullied |title=Spider-Man Homecoming Tom Holland Talks Being Bullied |access-date=2017-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170716071102/http://people.com/movies/spider-man-homecoming-tom-holland-talks-being-bullied/ |archive-date=2017-07-16 |url-status=live }}</ref>。溫布爾登學院之後，就讀[[克羅伊登|克羅伊登]]的{{le|BRIT學校|BRIT School}}<ref name="sct"/>。十幾歲的霍蘭德正值演藝事業缺乏水花之時，曾在威爾斯[[加的夫|加的夫]]短暫上過木工學校<ref>{{Citation|title=How Tom Holland Drunkenly Saved Spider-Man|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1-NPFORuPCw|language=en|access-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205223443/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1-NPFORuPCw|archive-date=2019-12-05|url-status=live}}</ref>。

七歲時被診斷出患有閱讀障礙。父母將他和兄弟們（以避免讓另外三個弟弟感到被忽視）送到一所私立學校，以得到必要的關照。然而，這開始對家庭經濟狀況產生負面影響，而霍蘭德對此現狀感到不滿。在學校的一堂課上，霍蘭德的母親看到了一則舞蹈課的廣告，決定幫孩子報名。<ref name="dyslexia">{{cite web |url=http://www.dominicholland.co.uk/dyslexia-is-in-the-news/ |title=Dyslexia is in the news... |work=DominicHolland.co.uk |first=Dominic |last=Holland |author-link=Dominic Holland |date=2014-02-26 |access-date=2018-09-30 |publisher=MMB Creative |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170817075352/http://www.dominicholland.co.uk/dyslexia-is-in-the-news/ |archive-date=2017-08-17 |url-status=live }}</ref>就學期間，霍蘭德是[[托定咸熱刺足球會|托定咸熱刺足球會]]的支持者<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tottenham fan @TomHolland1996 wants a @SpursOfficial-@BrentfordFC Champions League Final|url=https://twitter.com/gqsports/status/1461021232539836425|access-date=2021-11-19|website=Twitter|language=en}}</ref>。

根據霍蘭德的說法，表演並不總是自己的職業選擇，只是一些緣故而繼續走下去。他引用了[[愛德華·諾頓|愛德華·諾頓]]在電影《[[一級恐懼|一級恐懼]]》（1996年）中的表演作​​為靈感：「我認為他在鏡頭前簡直完美，表演上沒有任何需要更加精進之處。」<ref name="variety">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/awards/tom-holland-cherry-awards-circuit-podcast-1234899695/|title=‘Cherry’ Star Tom Holland Talks Getting an Itch for Directing and ‘Spider-Man 3’ Is ‘Most Ambitious Superhero Film of All Time’|last=Davis|first=Clayton|work=Variety|date=2021-02-04|accessdate=2022-02-16}}</ref>長大後，身為[[蜘蛛人|蜘蛛人]]粉絲的他擁有該角的30套服裝<ref>{{cite news |last1=Khomami |first1=Nadia |title=From Billy Elliot to Spider-Man: how Tom Holland won the world’s heart |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2022/jan/24/tom-holland-actor-billy-elliot-to-spider-man |access-date=2022-02-13 |work=The Guardian |date=2022-01-24 |language=en}}</ref>。

